2022 was a good one. Played some shows. Wrote a bunch of new songs. Hunted a lot and harvested my first deer. Drank good beer. Traveled to some cool places. Attended my first Preds game. Lots of home projects. Hosted Hibachi night. Sister got married. Spent some quality time with family and friends.

Feel incredibly fortunate for the experiences and perspective that 2022 provided. Can’t wait to conquer the new year! Wish you all a blessed new year 🤙🏼

#endofyear #2022recap #newyearseve2022 #newyear #happynewyear #2022reelsrecap

Welcome to the world, Hunter James Miller. @sam_saint_miller was an absolute trooper! This is a chapter we’ve been looking forward to for a while and we feel blessed to have a healthy baby boy in our life.

#millerlite #itsmillertime #wearethemillers

I was fortunate enough to land this guy this past weekend. Grateful to put some meat in the freezer and thankful I could call good people like @barrykyork to help me haul him out. 

Growing up by the ocean and being an avid waterman most of my life I’m naturally big on conservation. Most people don’t realize hunting is an important form of conservation and fail to educate themselves.

I posted some hunting related content last year that went viral on social media and it made me realize I needed to take a  step back from social media and take a breather. Hence why I haven’t posted much outside of a handful of IG stories here and there. 

It felt good. 

I’m happy I did. I was busy writing songs and enjoying time with my family.

Now I’m back. 

Hope you’re still along for the ride 🤙🏼

#hunting #huntingseason #whitetail #bowhunting #bowhunter #hunttn
